        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 2. Pericelis flavomarginata sp. nov. Photographs of a living specimen (A–C) and a specimen after being cleared in xylene (D); sketch of eyespot distribution (E). A. ICHUM 6116 (holotype), entire animal, dorsal view. B. ICHUM 6116 (holotype), entire animal, ventral view. C. ICHUM 6122 (paratype), magnification of tentacles. D. ICHUM 6122 (paratype), magnification of anterior body. E. Cerebral, frontal, marginal, and tentacular eyespots distribution.Abbreviations: ce, cerebral eyespots; cg, cement glands; fe, frontal eyespots; me, marginal eyespots; ph, pharynx; t, marginal tentacles; te, tentacular eyespots. Scale bars: A, B, 5 mm; C–E, 1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4315930/files/figure.png" .

